0031c81064c705ad124f697774391c","tid":2289462,"uid":188515,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T09:24:49.000Z","msg":"泰國國會今天起一連兩天辯論6個由朝野政黨提出以及一個由公民團體iLaw提出的修憲草案版本，學生抗議團體號召支持者包圍國會，直到國會議員接受民間版本為止。示威者下午衝擊警方在國會外設置的路障，防暴警方射水炮阻止。<br />\n<br />\n示威者要求政府修改憲法、改革王室及總理巴育下台，警方在國會外設置鐵絲網路障，不准學生接近國會50米範圍，但戴上頭盔、面罩的學生發動衝擊，試圖拆除路障，警員便發射水炮阻止，學生投擲顏色煙霧彈還擊。<br />\n泰國警方之前已曾兩度出動水炮驅趕示威者，分別是上月16日及本月8日。上月16日總理約2,000示威者與警方爆發衝突，防暴警出動水炮車向僅以傘陣抵擋的示威者發射水炮，現場一片混亂，更有僧侶挺身而出，上前向水炮車拍打車門，呼籲防暴警停手，示威者在警方出動水炮後，宣佈示威活動結束。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LFxxZ4y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLFxxZ4y.jpg&h=2bc9d52a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qMt1Tpy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqMt1Tpy.jpg&h=e5945635&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b1ae0c2ae8d7f346073147d20107b5d689ada1bc","tid":2289462,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T09:25:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5dfee0ea6594f8f4e27bcb1ba9c8ec73e4261d29","tid":2289462,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T09:25:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88231f1096a12f4e415c59ad90c10674bfb9c61f","tid":2289462,"uid":30084,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T09:25:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TeCVdpT.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTeCVdpT.gif&h=3f22f0df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"292fbfcfb867f735227f1bdec30c6f6de9d5217d","tid":2289462,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T09:27:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9a7a1f9f8701f0128f58994caa083f917d7fb56","tid":2289462,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T09:30:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"